# Accessibility Checklist – CivicaID

✔ High contrast color themes  
✔ Font sizes meet WCAG AA for seniors  
✔ Voice-first interface for blind users  
✔ Vibration feedback for tactile confirmation  
✔ Full captioning and visual alerts for deaf users  
✔ Simplified navigation with large buttons  
✔ Audio cues supplemented with visual equivalents  
✔ Touch targets minimum 44px  
✔ Emergency mode bypass for authorized personnel  
✔ Clear reading order and consistent UI structure  
